code: static String getQualifiedName(Element element) {     if (element != null) {         TypeElement enclosingElement = getEnclosingTypeElement(element.asType()).         if (enclosingElement != null) {             return getQualifiedName(enclosingElement) + "$" + ((DeclaredType) element.asType()).asElement().getSimpleName().toString().         }         if (element instanceof TypeElement) {             return ((TypeElement) element).getQualifiedName().toString().         }     }     return null. }

private static TypeElement getEnclosingTypeElement(TypeMirror type) {     if (type instanceof DeclaredType) {         DeclaredType declaredType = (DeclaredType) type.         Element enclosingElement = declaredType.asElement().getEnclosingElement().         if (enclosingElement != null && enclosingElement instanceof TypeElement) {             return (TypeElement) enclosingElement.         }     }     return null. }
